reviewText: i was very impressed by the close ups camera work of these jets.
I have enjoyed this product very much. I'd be interested in buying more of these kind of videos. Thank you so much!

I loved the DVDs really interesting my favorite ones were the F/A-18 Hornet, F-14 and F-15. I think these were the best DVDs Topics has made, So the DVDs were great but the box was HORRIBLE it was packed all together in one i thought it would be those DVD boxes but they were not,I was checking to see if there were any scratches but there were a little bit but they all worked. Anyways the DVDS  were GREAT

Fighter Pilot DVD get us a very good information. Almost all discs has very good photography but one disc (F-15) has old films and some scene appear twice or three times. In general I like this product.
